title: Tajikistan Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Tajikistan increased to 32711.95 TJS Thousand in August from 32086.22 TJS Thousand in July of 2022. Money Supply M2 in Tajikistan averaged 6568.43 TJS Thousand from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 32711.95 TJS Thousand in August of 2022 and a record low of 93.89 TJS Thousand in January of 2001. Tajikistan Money Supply M2 includes M1 plus short-term time deposits in banks. This page provides - Tajikistan Money Supply M2 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bank of Tajikistan
